# CountDown App Project Structure

## iOS App
The main iOS app is located in the `countDown` directory. Key files include:

- [countDownApp.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/countDownApp.swift) - Main app entry point
- [Event.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/Models/Event.swift) - Event model definition
- [EventRow.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/EventRow.swift) - Event list row view
- [EventDetailView.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/EventDetailView.swift) - Event detail view
- [CountdownDisplay.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/CountdownDisplay.swift) - Countdown display component
- [EventColor.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/EventColor.swift) - Color definitions for events

## Landing Page
The landing page is in the `LP` directory:

- [index.html](mdc:LP/index.html) - Main landing page (Japanese)
- [support.html](mdc:LP/support.html) - Support page (Japanese)
- [support.en.html](mdc:LP/support.en.html) - Support page (English)
- [privacy_policy.html](mdc:LP/privacy_policy.html) - Privacy policy
- [terms_of_service.html](mdc:LP/terms_of_service.html) - Terms of service

## Configuration
- [firebase.json](mdc:LP/firebase.json) - Firebase hosting configuration
- [GoogleService-Info.plist](mdc:countDown/countDown/GoogleService-Info.plist) - Firebase configuration for iOS app

